data.description: Located in the highly desired neighborhood of Harbor View in Smithville, Missouri. This beautiful family home is a must see!  Sitting at the end of a cul-de-sac, this spacious 5 Bedroom 3 1/2 bath has a paved trail from the extended back yard directly to the Smithville Lake.  Its neighborhood park/pool is less than a five minute walk away from the house. To top that, it's only minutes away from the new Smithville dog park, the dam, walking/biking trails, a football field and a picnic/park area. The home is also in district for the new and updated Smithville school and just quick drive from historical downtown Smithville. This is the perfect spot for a growing family that enjoys time outside and hosting for the holidays.
